					<div class="commentheading">On November 08, 2009 at 12:12 PM, Pete (guest) said...</div>
					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Here's a real winner and its easy to make!</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody">4   cups powdered sugar <br />
1/4   cup milk <br />
1/2   cup Butter, softened <br />
2   teaspoons vanilla <br />
   Food color, if desired <br />
<br />
Combine all ingredients except food color in large bowl. Beat at low speed until well mixed. Increase speed to medium; beat, scraping bowl often, until light and fluffy. Tint frosting with food color, if desired.<br />
<br />
Enjoy</div>
