					<div class="commentheading">On June 22, 2010 at 06:36 PM, Dilbert said...</div>
					<div class="commentsubject"></div>
					<div class="commentbody">sounds like the sugar did not thoroughly dissolve - that happens as you mix the sugar and eggs together - the water in the eggs is what dissolves the sugar.  my guess is you may have gone through that stage a bit too fast.<br />
<br />
you could try "superfine" sugar - it has finer crystals that dissolve more readily.</div>
					<hr size="1" noshade />
				
